episodes.title: Former member of SoCal religious group with alleged ties to two deaths speaks out
episodes.description:
A former member of the Inland Empire-based His Way Spirit Led Assemblies is speaking out after several of the leaders of the religious group were charged with two murders on Monday. Mike Rogers reports.

episodes.title: Murder charges filed against leaders of SoCal religious group connected to multiple missing people
episodes.description:
Murder charges were filed on Monday against multiple members of the Southern California-based religious group called "His Way Spirit Led Assemblies," which has been connected to multiple missing people in recent months. Mike Rogers reports.

episodes.title: Inland Empire religious group tied to Colton boy's 2010 death
episodes.description:
Colton Police said the religious group "His Way Spirit Led Assemblies" had temporary custody of the 4-year-old when he died. Jasmine Viel reports.

episodes.title: Investigators say two men gone missing in recent years were with same Inland Empire religious group
episodes.description:
Police say that new leads revealed another man with the same Inland Empire religious organization was reported missing in 2019, and that at least one of the disappearances is being investigated as a homicide. Mike Rogers reports.
